The paper deals with a robotic vehicle tasked with gathering information, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The paper also discusses the robot's ability to perform computations for inference and planning, which suggests a focus on artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also considers the robot's maneuvering capabilities, which falls under the category of control systems (cs.SY). The paper also discusses the amount and distribution of information that can be acquired at each data source, which suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.MA) and information theory (cs.IT).
